```plantuml
@startuml aws-solutions_iot-device-simulator

actor User
participant "Web UI" as WebUI
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Microservices Lambda" as MicroLambda
participant "Simulator Lambda" as SimLambda
participant "AWS IoT Core" as IoTCore
participant "Step Functions" as StepFunc
participant "DynamoDB" as DDB
participant "CloudWatch" as CW

User -> WebUI: Access Device Simulator
WebUI -> APIGW: HTTP Request (Create/Start Simulation)
APIGW -> MicroLambda: Invoke (API Request)
MicroLambda -> DDB: CRUD Operations (Device Types/Simulations)
MicroLambda --> APIGW: API Response
APIGW --> WebUI: Display Status

MicroLambda -> StepFunc: Start Execution (Simulation Workflow)
StepFunc -> SimLambda: Invoke (Device Simulation)
SimLambda -> IoTCore: Connect/Publish MQTT Messages
IoTCore --> SimLambda: ACK
SimLambda -> CW: Log Metrics
SimLambda --> StepFunc: Execution Status
StepFunc --> MicroLambda: Workflow Completion

@enduml
```